IMAPStore gmail-remote
Host imap.gmail.com
User christoffer143@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass show mutt"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt


MaildirStore gmail-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/.local/share/mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/gmail/INBOX

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Create Both
Expunge Both
Patterns * ![Gmail]* "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Starred" "[Gmail]/All Mail"
SyncState *


IMAPStore postau-remote
Host post.au.dk
User au618187
PassCmd "pass show web/au.dk | head -n1"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt


MaildirStore postau-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/.local/share/mail/postau/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/postau/INBOX

Channel postau
Far :postau-remote:
Near :postau-local:
Create Both
Expunge Both
Patterns *
SyncState *

